import { Box, Button, FormControl, Input, Stack } from "@chakra-ui/react";

export function LoginForm() {
  return (
    <>
    <Box></Box>
      <FormControl isRequired>
        <Input placeholder="email" />
        <Input
          placeholder="password"
          type="password"
        />
        <Button
          width='full'
          mt={4}
          colorScheme='blue'
          size="md">
          Acessar
        </Button>
      </FormControl>
    </>
  )
}
